title: r/Choosingbeggars WHY DOES THIS BEACH HAVE TOO MUCH SAND?
description:
r/Choosingbeggars In today's video, OP posts a huge lists of complaints that people have about a luxury vacation at a tropical resort. And believe it or not, some people actually complain that the beach is too sandy. Lady, what were you expecting at a beach? Dirt? If you like this video and want to see more, hit the subscribe button for daily Reddit content!
